WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:00.089
BOOM!

00:00.089 --> 00:00.624
The desert sand explodes as David

00:00.624 --> 00:06.096
Ben-Gurion emerges, a figure of unwavering
resolve.

00:06.096 --> 00:06.555
"I am inevitable!

00:06.555 --> 00:07.320
" he proclaims, his voice

00:07.320 --> 00:08.565
ringing with conviction.

00:08.565 --> 00:10.224
The British Mandate dissolves

00:10.224 --> 00:12.939
into a puff of comic smoke.

00:12.939 --> 00:13.392
KA-POW!

00:13.392 --> 00:14.736
Independence is declared, sweat beading on
his

00:14.736 --> 00:19.008
brow as a new nation is born.

00:19.008 --> 00:19.107
WHOOSH!

00:19.107 --> 00:19.704
Even amidst the intense pressure of

00:19.704 --> 00:27.312
cabinet meetings, Ben-Gurion maintains his
serene yoga

00:27.312 --> 00:32.400
posture, a picture of calm amidst the

00:32.400 --> 00:33.127
storm.

00:33.127 --> 00:37.488
Kirby Dots energy powers the rapid

00:37.488 --> 00:38.832
construction of kibbutzim across the newly
formed

00:38.832 --> 00:39.120
land.

00:39.120 --> 00:40.848
He retires to a tranquil desert

00:40.848 --> 00:42.528
cabin, a single thought bubble above his

00:42.528 --> 00:42.720
head:

00:42.720 --> 00:43.104
"Finally, peace.

00:43.104 --> 00:44.064
" But the legend is

00:44.064 --> 00:44.702
not yet complete.

00:44.702 --> 00:45.339
"Ben-Gurion will return...

00:45.339 --> 00:45.552
in

00:45.552 --> 00:45.762
1955!

00:45.762 --> 00:46.602
" True Believer Achievement:

00:46.602 --> 00:47.232
Created an Entire

00:47.232 --> 00:47.544
Country.

